          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is a real risk, something two alleged car thieves learned the hard way in Benton County, Washington. After getting rescued by some deputies, they got special bracelets and a free ride.",
